---
By: Peace Pilgrim
Locus:
  Page: 358
  Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Perfection
---
Inner peace is not found by staying on the surface of life, or by
attempting to escape from life through any means. Inner peace is found by
facing life squarely, solving its problems, and delving as far beneath the
surface as possible to discover its verities and realities.
